text: Gunnar Böös (30 May 1894 - 4 February 1987) was a Swedish fencer. He competed in the individual foil event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1894 births Category:1987 deaths Category:Swedish male fencers Category:Swedish foil fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Sweden Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lund
